title: For Sale:  Complete 37mm Launcher & Reloading Supplies
postcontent:
Up for sale is my absolutely badass, safe queen of a project, never fired, never used.

37MM Launcher, with a full stock system, as well as flip up sites. This is one bad ass little launcher, that does not require any special license to own. 

This package includes the following:

- 1x rail mountable 12inch 37mm launcher. Yes, this can can mount on your AR
- 1x 37mm 12 inch rail stock system. It makes this a standalone system
- 5x 3.5 inch aluminum hulls, for reloading your own rounds (uses shotgun #209 primer)
- 5x mini-MOAB projectile, unfused (1x head, 1x bottom, and 1x fin)
- 5x mini-MOAB projectile, fused  (1x head, 1x bottom, and 1x fin)
- Reloading instructions
- ONE SUPER BADASS PIECE OF EQUIPMENT

Parts are CAD designed and CNC machined from solid billet material rather than the typical stamped and welded construction of other launchers. The 6061 T-6 aircraft grade aluminum components are anodized in a non-glare matte black finishing for maximum durability and ease of maintenance. 

Additional components are built from 1018 cold rolled steel and plated with a mil-spec black oxide finish. The proprietary STZ push button cylindrical breech lock design is 3 times stronger than existing lever lock systems. The Havoc is designed to mount on any mil spec rail system. Installation simply requires sliding the launcher onto the bottom rail of the handguard and tightening two set screws which are included.

This is one of those things that makes gun lovers get a little wet. Its a non-restricted item, marked for use with gas, pepper, and smoke rounds. Any other round would require you to declare this a destructive device with the ATF, and get a stamp for it.

No powder or primers are included. This is just the parts and pieces.

This was a project I put together, then put down. I really love it, but I just don't have the time to put into this anymore. Save yourself a grip of time and research with this really beautiful set.

Open to trades, partial trades, but cash is preferred. Or best offer.

NOTE: No powder or primers are included. This is just the parts and pieces.

If you want to have this turned into a registered destructive device, you must first get a serial number engraved onto it, then apply with the ATF. 

These are all brand new parts and pieces, never used.
